A. Yes.

Q. And you knew he was tired when you took that interview, did you
not?

A. Yeah.

I knew I was, too.

Q. So you were both tired, right?

A. Yes.

Q. Okay.

MR. P. BAKER: Exhibit 782.

MR. BAKER: We don't need this reported because there's a transcript of
