A. Yes, it was.

Q. Outside of Mr. Simpson's house?

A. Yes.

Q. Okay.

Looking at the black sweat pants that Mr. Simpson's wearing in Exhibit
2220, are those the black sweat pants that you acquired for him?

A. Yes, they are.

MS. MOLINARO: And the next one, Steve, this will be marked next, 2226,
put that on the monitor.

Q. (BY MS. MOLINARO) Tell me, do you recognize the person in that
