A. Three, three and a half years.

Q. How many times had you been to Mr. Simpson's house to pick him up,
if you can approximate, as of June 12, 1994?

A. Hundred times.

Q. Was there ever -- ever a single occasion when you came to pick Mr.
Simpson up, that he was not home?

