MR. PETROCELLI: Beyond the scope, Your Honor.

THE COURT: Overruled.

There's no relationship with regard to this.

Q. (BY MR. BAKER) That's true, is it not?

A. Yes.

Q. Mr. Marlow also investigated the case at the direction and through
