at that time to serve Mr. Kardashian, and that he was out of town; he
would be back last Saturday or Sunday. And she discussed with him his
appearance. We talked about his appearing Wednesday morning to
testify, the scope of his examination, and whether or not she was
going to appear with him.

And she never -- she indicated to me there was no reason to serve him
at that time.

I expressed a willingness to do so. She asked to hold off as a
courtesy.

It was only yesterday, at 2:30 in the afternoon, that she left a
message in my New York office that he would not appear without a
