A. I did one more job after that. It wasn't really a job, though.

Q. Actually, in 1995, you appeared nude in Cigar Aficionado magazine,
did you not?

MR. KELLY: Objection, relevance.

THE COURT: You opened it. Overruled.

Q. (BY MR. BAKER) Did you not?

A. Yeah. That was the one job I was talking about.

Q. And you certainly wanted the limelight if you appeared without any
