A. No. I can't really work with a big belly anyway. I'm getting ready
to have another baby, so...

Q. And you had already had how many babies when you appeared without
clothes on in Cigar Aficionado magazine?

A. I had had one, and had one on the way, actually.

MR. BAKER: Thank you. Nothing further.

MR. KELLY: Nothing further, Your Honor.

