A. He said that he wanted --

MR. LEONARD: Objection, Your Honor. Object to the hearsay.

THE COURT: That's overruled.

THE WITNESS: The question again?

Q. I'm sorry.

What, if anything, did Mr. Simpson say and/or do after you observed
