<H2>The O.J. Simpson Civil Trial Transcripts: October</H2>

<P>NOTE: Some of these files are quite long (200k+) and may take a few minutes to load. If you prefer, you may download a compressed (zipped) version of the file to your hard drive. (You'll need an <A HREF="/download/utility/">unzipping utility</A> to decompress the file).</P>

<HR WIDTH=525 ALIGN=LEFT>

<P><A HREF="oct23.html"><B>Wednesday, October 23</B></A><BR>
<I><A HREF="oct23.zip">Download a zipped version</A></I><BR>
Attorneys for the plaintiffs begin their opening statements on the first day of the civil trial.</P>

<P><A HREF="oct24.html"><B>Thursday, October 24</B></A><BR>
<I><A HREF="oct24.zip">Download a zipped version</A></I><BR>
Defense lawyer attacks Nicole Brown Simpson's character.</P>

<P><A HREF="oct25.html"><B>Friday, October 25</B></A><BR>
<I><A HREF="oct25.zip">Download a zipped version</A></I><BR>
Plaintiffs begin their case with timeline witnesses.<BR>
<I><B>Witnesses:</B> Karen Crawford, Stewart Tanner, Robert Heidstra, Louis Karpf, Steven Schwab, Sukru Boztepe</I></P>

<P><A HREF="oct28.html"><B>Monday, October 28</B></A><BR>
<I><A HREF="oct28.zip">Download a zipped version</A></I><BR>
Police describe the crime scene at Nicole Brown Simpson's condominium.<BR>
<I><B>Witnesses:</B> Robert Riske, Michael Terrazas, David Rossi</I></P>

<P><A HREF="oct29.html"><B>Tuesday, October 29</B></A><BR>
<I><A HREF="oct29.zip">Download a zipped version</A></I><BR>
More police witnesses, including Ron Phillips telling his part of the story of the finding of the bloody glove.<BR>
<I><B>Witnesses:</B> David Rossi, Donald Thompson, Ron Phillips</I></P>

<P><B>Wednesday, October 30</B><BR>
No Transcript; Court not in session.</P>

<P><A HREF="oct31.html"><B>Thursday, October 31</B></A><BR>
<I><A HREF="oct31.zip">Download a zipped version</A></I><BR>
Testimony from retired LAPD Detective Tom Lange.<BR>
<I><B>Witnesses:</B> Thomas Lange</I></P>

<HR WIDTH=525 ALIGN=LEFT>

