<H2>Small Business Seminars</H2>

<P><A HREF="http://www.counsel.com/spotlight/telecom/telecom.htm">What the Telecommunications Reform Bill Means for You</A><BR>
How will you be affected by the new telecommunications reform legislation? Telecom experts explain the details in an online seminar, reprinted from our affiliate service for lawyers, Counsel Connect. You can also read the <A HREF="http://www.technologylaw.com/techlaw/act.html">full text of the bill</A>.</P> 

<P><A HREF="compliance/">Corporate Compliance Seminar</A><BR>
Seminar transcript, 10/23/95 through 11/10/95: Lawyers on <A HREF="http://www.counsel.com/lawlinks/about.htm">Counsel Connect</A> consider different methods for complying with federal, state and local laws and regulations. Discussion includes analysis of the <A HREF="http://www.ncpl.org/~ncpl">National Center for Preventive Law's</A> twenty principles of corporate compliance, and how they achieve their goal of preventing problems under the <A HREF="http://www.eff.org/pub/Legal/sentencing_guidelines.amend">Federal Sentencing Guidelines</A> for Organizations.</P>

<P><A HREF="handbook/">The Ultimate Employee Handbook - A Workshop</A><BR>
The legal experts on <A HREF="http://www.counsel.com/lawlinks/about.htm">Counsel Connect</A> discuss the elements that make up this essential tool for businesses of all sizes. Includes a <A HREF="handbook/index.html#library">library</A> of sample handbook language.</P>
