<html><TITLE> Court TV Presents - Ancestral Exclusion</TITLE><body bgcolor=ffffff vlink=ff0000><center><img width=517 height=142 src=/graphics/ctv/chall.gif></center>␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀<blockquote><H2>Ancestral Exclusion</H2><b>It is 1942. Fred Korematsu, an American citizen of Japanese ancestry, is arrested and convicted of violating an exclusion order that made it illegal for him to enter or remain in the military area of San Leandro, California.<p>With the help of the ACLU, Korematsu has challenged his conviction. His challenge has made its way to the Supreme Court. He claims the exclusion order violates his right to due process and equal protection under the U.S. Constitution.  The Solicitor General, arguing for the United States, argues that the exclusion order is a valid exercise of the war powers of Congress. Who should win?</B><P> <a name="tab"><H2>First. . .</H2></a><font size=+1> <br clear=left><B><img width=33 height=31 align=middle src=/graphics/ctv/button.gif alt=" * "><a href="casef2.htm">Review Background and Context</a><br clear=left><img width=33 height=31 align=middle src=/graphics/ctv/button.gif alt=" * "><a href="casef3.htm">Get More Facts</a><br clear=left><img width=33 height=31 align=middle src=/graphics/ctv/button.gif alt=" * "><a href="casef4.htm">Review Legal Doctrine and Authorities</a><br clear=left><img width=33 height=31 align=middle src=/graphics/ctv/button.gif alt=" * "><a href="casef5.htm">Consider Possible Arguments</a><br clear=left><H2>Then. . .</H2><img width=33 height=31 align=middle src=/graphics/ctv/button.gif alt=" * "><B><a href="argue.htm">Present an Argument for One Side or the Other</a></b><br clear=left></font><H2>Or. . .</H2><img width=33 height=31 align=middle src=/graphics/ctv/redbutt.gif alt=" * "><B> <a href="casef6.htm">Decide the case for Mr. Korematsu</a><br><img width=33 height=31 align=middle src=/graphics/ctv/redbutt.gif alt=" * "><a href="casef7.htm">Decide the case for The Solicitor General</a></font></B><br clear=left></font><H4><a href=/cases/direct.htm><I>Brief Instructions</i></a></H4><P><a  href=/cases/><I>Courtroom Challenge home</I></a></blockquote><P ALIGN=CENTER><IMG SRC="/graphics/ctv/stroke.gif" HEIGHT=15 WIDTH=547><BR><A HREF="/map/bottom.map"><IMG SRC="/graphics/ctv/bottom.gif" ISMAP ALIGN=ABSBOTTOM BORDER=0 WIDTH=533 HEIGHT=30></A><BR><IMG SRC="/graphics/ctv/rights.gif" ALT="All Materials Copyright CourtTV 1995. All Rights Reserved. Disclaimer: Nothing in this site is intended to constitute legal advice"></P></body></html>
