<html><title>Court TV Presents - Takings on the Beach</title><body bgcolor=ffffff vlink=ff0000>␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀<center><img width=517 height=142 src=/graphics/ctv/chall.gif></center> <blockquote><H2>Takings on the Beach</H2> <B>In 1986, Mr. Lucas spent almost $1 million for two vacant beach lots on the Isle of Palms in South Carolina. He intended to build a house on each lot, one for his family and one for resale.<p>Two years later, the South Carolina legislature passed a statute prohibiting building within a stated distance from the shore, to prevent beach erosion. In light of the shape of his previously buildable lots, Mr. Lucas was prevented from building any houses.<p>Mr. Lucas sued the State, claiming that the statute resulted in an unconstitutional "taking" of his property. Who should win?</B><P> <a name="tab"><H2>First. . .</H2></a><font size=+1><B><img width=33 height=31 align=middle src=/graphics/ctv/button.gif alt=" * "><a href="casef2.htm">Review Background and Context</a><br clear=left><img width=33 height=31 align=middle src=/graphics/ctv/button.gif alt=" * "><a href="casef3.htm">Get More Facts</a><br clear=left><img width=33 height=31 align=middle src=/graphics/ctv/button.gif alt=" * "><a href="casef4.htm">Review Other Cases and Authorities</a><br clear=left><img width=33 height=31 align=middle src=/graphics/ctv/button.gif alt=" * "><a href="casef5.htm">Consider Possible Arguments</a><br clear=left><H2>Then. . .</H2><img width=33 height=31 align=middle src=/graphics/ctv/button.gif alt=" * "><a href="argue.htm">Present an Argument for One Side or the Other</a></B><br clear=left></font><H2>Or. . .</H2><img width=33 height=31 align=middle src=/graphics/ctv/redbutt.gif alt=" * "><B><font size=+1><a href="casef6.htm">Decide the case for Mr. Lucas</a><br clear=left><img width=33 height=31 align=middle src=/graphics/ctv/redbutt.gif alt=" * "><font size=+1><a href="casef7.htm">Decide the case for the State</a></font></B><br clear=left></font></font></font><H4><a href=/cases/direct.htm><I>Brief Instructions</I></a></H4><P><a  href=/cases/><I>Courtroom Challenge home</I></a> </blockquote><P ALIGN=CENTER><IMG SRC="/graphics/ctv/stroke.gif" HEIGHT=15 WIDTH=547><BR><A HREF="/map/bottom.map"><IMG SRC="/graphics/ctv/bottom.gif" ISMAP ALIGN=ABSBOTTOM BORDER=0 WIDTH=533 HEIGHT=30></A><BR><IMG SRC="/graphics/ctv/rights.gif" ALT="All Materials Copyright CourtTV 1995. All Rights Reserved. Disclaimer: Nothing in this site is intended to constitute legal advice"></P></BODY></html>
