<html><TITLE> Court TV Presents: Suspicionless Drug Tests</TITLE><bodybgcolor=ffffff vlink=ff0000><center><img width=517 height=142 src=/graphics/ctv/chall.gif></center>␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀<blockquote><H2>Vernonia High - Suspicionless Drug Tests</H2><b> In 1989, the school district in Vernonia, Oregon began random drug testing ofstudent athletes and required all students wishing to participate in sports tosign a form consenting to the testing. If they did not, they were barred fromparticipation. In the fall of 1991, seventh grader James Acton wanted to try outfor the football team, but refused to sign the consent form. He was kicked offthe team.<P>Acton, through his parents, filed suit, claiming that suspicionless drug testingamounts to an unreasonable search under the Fourth Amendment. The school districtsays such testing of students is reasonable. Who should win?<a name="tab"><H2>First. . .</H2></a><font size=+1> <br clear=left><B> <img width=33 height=31 align=middle src=/graphics/ctv/button.gif alt=" * "> <ahref=case2.htm>Review Background  Information</a><br clear=left> <img width=33 height=31 align=middle src=/graphics/ctv/button.gif alt=" * "> <ahref=case3.htm>Get More Facts</a><br clear=left><img width=33 height=31 align=middle src=/graphics/ctv/button.gif alt=" * "> <ahref=case4.htm>Review Other Cases and Authorities</a><br clear=left><img width=33 height=31 align=middle src=/graphics/ctv/button.gif alt=" * "> <ahref=case5.htm>Consider Possible Arguments</a><br clear=left><H2>Then. . .</H2><img width=33 height=31 align=middle src=/graphics/ctv/button.gif alt=" * "><B><a href=argue.htm>Present an Argument for One Side or the Other</a></B><brclear=left></font><H2>Or. . .</H2><img width=33 height=31 align=middle src=/graphics/ctv/redbutt.gif alt=" * "><B><a href=case7.htm>Decide the case for James Acton</a></B><br clear=left><img width=33 height=31 align=middle src=/graphics/ctv/redbutt.gif alt=" * "><B><a href=case6.htm>Decide the case for the School District</a></font></B><brclear=left></font><P><a  href=/cases/><I>Return to main page</I></a> </blockquote><P ALIGN=CENTER><IMG SRC="/graphics/ctv/stroke.gif" HEIGHT=15 WIDTH=547><BR><A HREF="/map/bottom.map"><IMG SRC="/graphics/ctv/bottom.gif" ISMAP ALIGN=ABSBOTTOM BORDER=0 WIDTH=533HEIGHT=30></A><BR><IMG SRC="/graphics/ctv/rights.gif" ALT="All Materials Copyright CourtTV 1995.All Rights Reserved. Disclaimer: Nothing in this site is intended to constitutelegal advice"></P></BODY></html> 
