<html><title>Court TV Presents - Affirmative Action on Trial</title><bodybgcolor=ffffff vlink=ff0000><center><img width=517 height=142 src=/graphics/ctv/chall.gif></center>␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀<blockquote><H2>Bakke - Affirmative Action on Trial</H2><b>It is 1973. Allan Bakke applies to medical school at the University of Californiaat Davis. Davis has a special admissions "Task Force" to review applications of racialand ethnic minorities, with the aim of increasing minority admissions to the school. Bakke,who is white, gets rejected, despite the fact that his grades and test scores were wellabove those of admitted minority applicants. <P>Bakke challenges the admissions program in court, claiming it violates the Equal Protection Clause of the Constitution? Who should win?</B><P> <a name="tab"><H2>First. . .</H2></a><font size=+1> <br clear=left><B><img width=33 height=31 align=middle src=/graphics/ctv/button.gif alt=" * "><ahref="casef2.htm">Review Background and Context</a><br clear=left><img width=33 height=31 align=middle src=/graphics/ctv/button.gif alt=" * "><ahref="casef3.htm">Get More Facts</a><br clear=left><img width=33 height=31 align=middle src=/graphics/ctv/button.gif alt=" * "><ahref="casef4.htm">Review Other Cases and Authorities</a><br clear=left><img width=33 height=31 align=middle src=/graphics/ctv/button.gif alt=" * "><ahref="casef5.htm">Consider Possible Arguments</a><br clear=left><H2>Then. . .</H2><img width=33 height=31 align=middle src=/graphics/ctv/button.gif alt=" * "><B><a href="argue.htm">Present an Argument for One Side or the Other</a><br clear=left></font><H2>Or. . .</H2><img width=33 height=31 align=middle src=/graphics/ctv/redbutt.gif alt=" * "><B><a href="casef6.htm">Decide the case for Allan Bakke</a><br><img width=33 height=31 align=middle src=/graphics/ctv/redbutt.gif alt=" * "><ahref="casef7.htm">Decide the case for the University</a></font></B><br clear=left></font><H4><a href=/cases/direct.htm><I>Brief Instructions</I></a></H4><a  href=/cases/><I>Courtroom Challenge home</I></a> </blockquote><P ALIGN=CENTER><IMG SRC="/graphics/ctv/stroke.gif" HEIGHT=15 WIDTH=547><BR><A HREF="/map/bottom.map"><IMG SRC="/graphics/ctv/bottom.gif" ISMAP ALIGN=ABSBOTTOM BORDER=0 WIDTH=533HEIGHT=30></A><BR><IMG SRC="/graphics/ctv/rights.gif" ALT="All Materials Copyright CourtTV 1995.All Rights Reserved. Disclaimer: Nothing in this site is intended to constitutelegal advice"></P></body></html>
