     <LI>Overview of Amended Rules 26 and 11.

	<LI>Disclosure in Federal District Court & the District of Columbia

	<LI>Disclosure in Personal Injury and Public Interest Cases
</UL><P>

<b>January 18 & 19</b><br>
Rediscovering Discovery II - Litigation Under the Revised Federal Rules of Civil Procedure -- Part 1<BR> (Legal Times)
<UL TYPE=DISC>
	<LI>A Judge's View & An Attorney's View


	<LI>Discovery of Expert Witnesses & Scientific Evidence

	<LI>Amended Rule 11

</UL><p>

