<TITLE>Court TV On The Air</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY TEXT="#000000" LINK="#000080" VLINK="#DD0000" BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">
<A HREF="/map/ontheair.map"><IMG SRC="/graphics/ctv/headers/ontheair.gif" ISMAP ALT="Court TV On the Air" BORDER="0"></A>
<h2>Inside America's Courts</h2>

<P>Court TV has launched a syndicated daily news program called <I>Court TV: Inside America's Courts,</I> covering our judicial system. The show airs at various times on approximately 100 stations nationwide and is the first daily news program devoted to courts and the law.</P>

<P>We'll cover the high-profile, celebrity cases, but we'll also bring you into courtrooms across the country for cases often more interesting than the ones that receive the most publicity and attention. In addition, we'll report breaking legal news events that other news organizations ignore.</P>

<P>Keep a look out for the show. It's <I>Court TV: Inside America's Courts.</I></P>

<P>Visit the <A HREF="http://www.incourt.com/"><I>Inside America's Courts</I>  website</A> for the latest information on the show, including <A HREF="http://www.incourt.com/iac/schedule.html">times and stations</A>.</P>

