<HtMl><head><title>Teen Court TV: Survey for What's the Verdict?</title></head><body bgcolor=ffffff vlink=ff0000 link=000080><P align=center> <A HREF="/teens/maps/tbuttons.map"><IMG SRC="/teens/graphics/theader5.gif" ISMAP BORDER="0"></A></P><br clear=all><P>
<blockquote>

<H2><I>What's the Verdict? </I> Survey</H2>

<P> This week we have an assault trial from Bridgeton, New Jersey, in which karate expert, Joseph Artesi, Jr., is charged with aggravated assault after he killed a man during a fight. Please <A HREF="/teens/programs/wtv/current/">read our preview</A> of the case before casting your vote.</P>

<P>What's your verdict? Do you think that:</P>

<FORM METHOD=POST ACTION="http://www.courttv.com/ctv-bin/chooser">
<INPUT TYPE="hidden" NAME="TYPE" VALUE="SURVEY">

<INPUT TYPE="hidden" NAME="TITLE" VALUE="surwtv10"> <INPUT TYPE="hidden" NAME="NUMBER" VALUE="1">
<OL type="A">
 <LI> <INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="1" VALUE="A">Artesi should be found guilty, OR
 <LI> <INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="1" VALUE="B">Artesi should be found not guilty.
</OL>
<Input TYPE=submit VALUE="Send">
</form>
<P>Tune in Saturday morning for the results, or check back here
next week.</P>
</blockquote>
