<B>SIMPSON:</B> No.<P>

<B>LANGE:</B> All right, then do it. Come on.<P>

<B>SIMPSON:</B> No.<P>

<B>LANGE:</B> Come on, you're scaring the hell out of those people and they're being stupid 	out there. I can see them on the TV.<P>

