<B>SIMPSON:</B> Oh - I just want to see my home.<P>

<B>LANGE:</B> You will. You will. You want to see your kids though, too, don't you? Huh?<P>

<B>SIMPSON:</B> I got pictures with me.<P>

<B>LANGE:</B> You have pictures?<P>

