<B>LANGE:</B> Okay, but how about the real thing? And your mom? All right? How about the real thing?<P>

<B>SIMPSON:</B> Ah - <P>

<B>LANGE:</B> They need you. Don't do this to them. Don't do this to them. You're going to break their hearts. They're young yet. Come on! How about Arnelle? Have you thought of Arnelle yet?<P>

<B>SIMPSON:</B> Huh?<P>

<B>LANGE:</B> Have you thought of Arnelle yet? She needs you.<P>

<B>SIMPSON:</B> Ah <P>

