<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT08-B38-130</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA022-000241-B037-465</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.courttv.com:80/casefiles/simpson/documents/rockbld.html 199.29.97.40 19970108050457 text/html 10427
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.1
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 05:14:26 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 27-Sep-96 19:25:01 GMT
