<DOCOLDNO>IA022-000241-B037-491</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.courttv.com:80/casefiles/simpson/documents/altrock.html 199.29.97.40 19970108050508 text/html 10069
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.1
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 05:14:42 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 18-Sep-96 17:00:51 GMT
Content-length: 9875
