Pamela EngA:\FAYE.TXT␀U␀␀␀j8␀␀␀␀␀␀␀j8␀␀U␀␀␀P;␀␀␀␀␀␀␀P;␀␀U␀␀␀=␀␀1␀␀␀␀␀␀=␀␀U␀␀␀␀4=␀␀␀␀␀␀␀4=␀␀)␀AutoOpen␀AAAZAO␀AAAZFS␀PayLoad␀␀␀AAAZAO␀␀AAAZFS␀␀PAYLOAD␀␀AUTOOPEN␀@HP LaserJet 4/4M␀LPT1:␀HPPCL5MS␀HP LaserJet 4/4M␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀@␀g␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀X␀␀X␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀@␀MSUDNHP LaserJet 4␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀;␀␀␀␀␀d␀
